title: Q&A with Daphne and Heath
description:
We have finally made it to 200 episodes! Make sure to check out the episode before this (200) on the murder of Janett Christmas, and the urban legend that followed.
Here's a Q&A where we answer a bunch of questions sent in by our listener over the past week.
Thank you everyone!
